"{\"uid\": \"pennlive.com-news-2024-07-paris-police-install-anti-terrorism-perimeter-ahead-of-the-olympics-opening-ceremony.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS - A special kind of iron curtain came down across central Paris on Thursday, with the beginning of an Olympic anti-terrorism perimeter along the banks of the River Seine sealing off a miles-long area to Parisians and tourists who had not applied in advance for a pass.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 64, \"end\": 69, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.9452520422780725e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 164, \"end\": 175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The words on many lips were \\\"QR code,\\\" the pass that grants access beyond snaking metal barriers that delineate the security zone set up to protect the Olympic Games' opening ceremony on July 26.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not know it started today,\\\" said Emmanuelle Witt, a 35-year-old communications freelancer who was stopped by police near the Alma bridge while biking across town.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuelle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.998736336940419e-19, \"text\": \"Emmanuelle\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuelle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuelle\"}, {\"begin\": 526, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ernst_Witt\", \"score\": 0.9959706230485735, \"rank\": 0.0031261194438732113, \"text\": \"Witt\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ernst_Witt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ernst_Witt\"}, {\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alma_Mahler\", \"score\": 0.760427906973285, \"rank\": 0.312326108192005, \"text\": \"Alma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alma_Mahler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alma_Mahler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She desperately went on her phone to fill out the online form to get her QR code, unaware that the vetting process could take several days.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those with the precious code - either on their phones or printed out on pieces of paper - passed smoothly past police checkpoints at gaps in the barriers taller than most people.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those without got mostly turned away - with no amount of grumbling and cajoling making officers budge.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's too much, that's over the top, that whole thing is a pain,\\\" grumbled Nassim Bennamou, a delivery man who was denied access to the street leading to Notre Dame Cathedral on his scooter.\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While authorities announced the code system last year and have been meeting with local residents for months to explain the restrictions, not everyone was aware.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Officers patiently explained to visitors without the pass how to reach iconic Paris monuments without going through the restricted zone.\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1511, \"end\": 1516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.9452520422780725e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had no idea we needed a QR code,\\\" said Takao Sakamoto, 55, who was denied access to the Eiffel Tower near the Bir Hakeim Metro station.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1616, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takao_Sakamoto\", \"score\": 0.9999998026910556, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Takao Sakamoto\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takao_Sakamoto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takao_Sakamoto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the other hand, visitors who were lucky enough to come across officers who leniently let them pass without QR codes and others who'd equipped themselves with them were treated to the sight of near-empty riverside boulevards that, in normal times, heave with traffic.\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no one around!\\\"\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"sang a happy cyclist on a street he had largely to himself.\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With police seemingly everywhere, another man walking past a riverside caf\\u00e9 with fewer than usual customers loudly quipped: \\\"You can leave your money and cell phones on the tables, there is definitely no thieves!\\\"\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's surreal, it really feels like we are the only ones here,\\\" said Sarah Bartnicka from Canada.\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2361, \"end\": 2366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Platt\", \"score\": 0.9123212809935163, \"rank\": 0.09329244372327936, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Platt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Platt\"}, {\"begin\": 2382, \"end\": 2388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999998503881, \"rank\": 1.451066476148312e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris has repeatedly suffered deadly extremist attacks, most notably in 2015.\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2393, \"end\": 2398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.9452520422780725e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Up to 45,000 police and gendarmes as well as 10,000 soldiers are being deployed for Olympic security.\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2572, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some business owners inside the security zone grumbled that sharply reduced foot-fall would hurt their bottom line.\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They have locked me up like a prisoner,\\\" said Raymond Pignol.\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2742, \"end\": 2749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Asquith\", \"score\": 0.9882653135887083, \"rank\": 0.011874024360487857, \"text\": \"Raymond\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Asquith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Asquith\"}, {\"begin\": 2750, \"end\": 2756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/St\\u00e9phane_Pignol\", \"score\": 0.9101295171701695, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pignol\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/St\\u00e9phane_Pignol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/St\\u00e9phane_Pignol\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His restaurant, L'Auberge Caf\\u00e9, near the Pont Neuf that spans the Seine, is just inside the metal fencing.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2824, \"end\": 2829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.67383119475367e-20, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The perimeter went into effect early Thursday morning and will last through the ceremony.\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As an exception, Paris has decided to hold the opening of its first Games in a century on the river rather than in a stadium, like previous host cities.\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 3110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2975, \"end\": 2980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.9452520422780725e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of the river security measures will be lifted after the show.\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Use of and/or registration on any portion of this site constitutes acceptance of ourUser Agreement, (updated 8/1/2024) and acknowledgement of ourPrivacy Policy,andYour Privacy Choices and Rights(updated 10/1/2025).\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92025Advance Local Media LLC.\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved (About Us).The material on this site may not be reproduced, distributed, transmitted, cached or otherwise used, except with the prior written permission of Advance Local.\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3609, \"end\": 3622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advance_Publications\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advance Local\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advance_Publications\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advance_Publications\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Community Rulesapply to all content you upload or otherwise submit to this site.\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"YouTube's privacy policyis availablehereandYouTube's terms of serviceis availablehere.\", \"from\": 3707, \"to\": 3793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3707, \"end\": 3714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 0.9999999997849045, \"rank\": 2.148417508180912e-10, \"text\": \"YouTube\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ad Choices\", \"from\": 3795, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": []}]}"